{"id":8665,"date":"2025-09-23T06:30:54","date_gmt":"2025-09-23T06:30:54","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/realtrips.in\/?post_type=trip&#038;p=8665"},"modified":"2025-11-27T12:10:35","modified_gmt":"2025-11-27T12:10:35","slug":"vietnam","status":"publish","type":"trip","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/trip\/vietnam\/","title":{"rendered":"VIETNAM"},"content":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":8822,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","destination":[112],"activities":[],"trip_types":[76],"difficulty":[],"trip_tag":[],"wptravelengine_custom_taxonomy_tripcategory":[78],"class_list":["post-8665","trip","type-trip","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","destination-experience-vietnam","trip_types-customized-international-tour","tripcategory-customized-international-tour"],"packages_ids":[8669],"trip_extras":[],"cut_off_time":{"enabled":false,"duration":0,"duration_unit":"days"},"booked-seats":[],"code":"WTE-8665","price":117777,"has_sale":false,"sale_price":0,"discount_percent":0,"currency":{"code":"INR","symbol":"&#8377;"},"duration":{"days":8,"nights":7,"duration_unit":"days","duration_type":"days"},"min_pax":1,"max_pax":"","discount_value":0,"discount_label":"&#8377;0 Off","primary_category":27,"available_times":{"type":"default","items":["2021-1-01","2021-2-01","2021-3-01","2021-4-01","2021-5-01","2021-6-01","2021-7-01","2021-8-01","2021-9-01","2021-10-01","2021-11-01","2021-12-01"]},"description":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Journey through a country where tradition meets modern charm. Cruise the emerald waters of Ha Long Bay, wander through Hanoi\u2019s lively old quarters, explore the ancient streets of Hoi An, and feel the vibrant energy of Ho Chi Minh City. With stunning landscapes, rich heritage, and mouthwatering cuisine, Vietnam promises an experience full of discovery and delight.<br><br><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->","cost_includes":"Return Economy Airfare BOM-BOM  \nVietnam Tourist E Visa  \nBOM - HANOI - DNANG - HO CHI MINH \u2013 BOM ( Airfare consider As of now it may be change ) \nAccommodation ( 7 Nights ) \nMeals As mentioned above (Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner)  \nEnglish-speaking Driver  \nAll Tickets For sightseeing as mention in above plan  \nTour & Transfers ( SIC\/PVT BASIS ) \nTravel Insurance \nTravel Goodies  ","cost_excludes":" Any meals other than those mentioned above included. \nGST 5% \nCompulsory tips tp guide ( 3 Usd pp\/pd) when PVT \nMeal Other than mention in inclusion. \nAny Personal expenses. \nAny portage at airports and hotels, tips, insurance, wine, mineral water, telephone charges, and all term of personal nature. \nVehicle for Shopping, any personal things. \nAny services not specifically mentioned in the inclusions. \nExpenses caused by factors beyond our control like rail and flight delays, roadblocks, political disturbances etc.","itineraries":[],"faqs":[{"title":"1. What is included in the Vietnam package? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Accommodation, airport transfers, guided sightseeing tours, intercity travel, and daily breakfast.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"2. Do Indian travelers need a visa for Vietnam? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Yes, Indians require an eVisa to enter Vietnam, which is simple to apply online.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"3. What are the must-visit destinations in Vietnam? ","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hanoi, Ha Long Bay, Hoi An, Da Nang, and Ho Chi Minh City are among the top highlights.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"},{"title":"4. How many days are ideal for exploring Vietnam?","content":"<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>6 to 8 days are recommended to cover the main cities and attractions comfortably.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->"}],"is_featured":false,"featured_image":{"width":374,"height":226,"file":"2025\/09\/vietnam-1.png","filesize":227926,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"vietnam-1-300x181.png","width":3